Depends: cracklib2, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}
Description: Test the strength of virtual hosting passwords
 This package contains a simple script to test each virtual host
 password to ensure they are secure.
 .
 The passwords tested are:
 .
 * FTP passwords
 * IMAP passwords
 .
 The password strength testing is achieved via cracklib2.
